'''沙姑马山'''是《[[郑和航海图|郑和航海图]]》中的[[忽鲁谟斯|忽鲁谟斯]]国回[[古里|古里]]国[[过洋牵星图|过洋牵星图]]<ref> {{Cite book | author = 向达(整理) | title = 郑和航海图 | edition = 1982年第2次印刷| series = 中外交通史籍丛刊 | location = 北京 | publisher = 中华书局 | date = 1961 | pages = 63 | unified = 11018-203 | language = zh }} </ref>以及《[[顺风相送|顺风相送]]》<ref> {{cite wikisource | title=两种海道针经 }} </ref>中的《古里往忽鲁谟斯·回针》所提及的地名。在《[[郑和航海图|郑和航海图]]》中的同一张图里亦作'''沙马姑山'''。《[[顺风相送|顺风相送]]》中的《各处州府山形水势深浅泥沙地礁石之图》还提到了'''沙姑山'''，而《古里往忽鲁谟斯》提到了'''姑马山'''，这两个名称是否等同于沙姑马山尚有争议。

中外学者对'''沙姑马山'''（以及'''沙姑山'''、'''姑马山'''）今为何处说法不一，但都推断其大致位于[[阿曼|阿曼]]'''东哈杰尔山脉'''一带。

==海米斯山说==
朱鉴秋和李万权认为“沙姑马山”与“姑马山”都是指'''海米斯山'''（{{lang|la|Jabal Khamīs}}{{coord|22|22|59|N|59|26|43|E|display=inline}}），其高度为883米。<ref> {{Cite book | author = 海军海洋测绘研究所; 大连海运学院航海史研究室 | title = 新编郑和航海图集 | location = 北京 | publisher = 人民交通出版社 | date = 1988 | pages = 81-82 | ISBN = 7-114-00229-7 | language = zh }} </ref>徐勝一和陳有志认同此说，并提出“沙姑山”是'''东哈杰尔山脉'''（{{lang|la|Al Ḩajar ash Sharqī}}）。<ref>{{Cite journal|author=徐勝一|author2=陳有志|url=http://www.geog.ntu.edu.tw/index.php/tw/journal/volumns/journal41-60/details/5/54/%E7%AC%AC41~60%E6%9C%9F-%E9%84%AD%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8A%E9%81%8E%E6%B4%8B%E7%89%BD%E6%98%9F%E5%9C%96%E3%80%8B%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%81%E5%BE%97%E6%8A%8A%E6%98%94%E8%88%87%E6%B2%99%E5%A7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E4%B9%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6?layout=print&tmpl=component&contentbuilder_download_file=377773f0e825f0137d43ed777b170dfc3bc6794f|title=鄭和《過洋牽星圖》及丁得把昔與沙姑馬山地理定位之研究|journal=地理學報（國立臺灣大學）|year=2008|volume=52|pages=93-114|access-date=2019-01-14|archive-date=2019-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114210336/http://www.geog.ntu.edu.tw/index.php/tw/journal/volumns/journal41-60/details/5/54/%E7%AC%AC41~60%E6%9C%9F-%E9%84%AD%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8A%E9%81%8E%E6%B4%8B%E7%89%BD%E6%98%9F%E5%9C%96%E3%80%8B%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%81%E5%BE%97%E6%8A%8A%E6%98%94%E8%88%87%E6%B2%99%E5%A7%91%E9%A6%AC%E5%B1%B1%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%86%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E4%B9%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6?layout=print&tmpl=component&contentbuilder_download_file=377773f0e825f0137d43ed777b170dfc3bc6794f|dead-url=no}}</ref>海米斯山位于东哈杰尔山脉的东南端。

==古赖亚特山说==
J.V.G. Mills认为“沙姑马山”是'''古赖亚特山'''（{{lang|la|Jabal Qurayyāt}}{{coord|23|09|15|N|58|43|19|E|display=inline}}）。<ref>{{Cite book | author = 马欢(原著); 冯承钧(校注); Mills, J.V.G.(编译) | title = 瀛涯胜览 'The Overall Survey of the Ocean's Shores' [1433] | location = London, UK | publisher = Cambridge University Press | date = 1970 | pages = 300 | ISBN = 9780521010320 | url = https://books.google.fi/books?id=DjQ9AAAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover | language = en | quote = Sha ku ma mountain [Jabal Quraiyat, 23°10'N, 58°44'E, in Arabia] | access-date = 2019-01-14 | archive-date = 2019-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190114210310/https://books.google.fi/books?id=DjQ9AAAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover | dead-url = no }}</ref>这座山位于东哈杰尔山脉北段，耸立在代盖干河（{{lang|la|Wādī Ḑayqah}}）即“魔鬼裂口”（{{lang|en|Devil's Gap}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.nizwa.net/oman/explorer/places/tayeen/tayeen.html |title = Dima wa'Tayeen's fascinating beauty |publisher = Nizwa.NET |language = en |accessdate = 2019-01-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190122200551/http://www.nizwa.net/oman/explorer/places/tayeen/tayeen.html |archive-date = 2019-01-22 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>的北侧，高1,899米。<ref>{{Cite book | author = National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency | title = Red Sea and the Persian Gulf | edition = 11th Edition | series = Pub. 172 Sailing Directions (Enroute) | location = Annapolis, MD, USA | publisher = ProStar Publications | date = 2006 | pages = 190 | ISBN = 9781577857556 | url = https://books.google.fi/books?id=3jHUwGEbjNQC&printsec=frontcover | language = en | access-date = 2019-01-14 | archive-date = 2019-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190114210308/https://books.google.fi/books?id=3jHUwGEbjNQC&printsec=frontcover | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==舍杰尔与古迈莱说==
周运中认为“沙姑马山”是“沙姑山”的讹记，后者取自'''舍杰尔角'''（{{lang|la|Ra’s ash Shajar / Ras Shagar}}{{coord|22|58|09|N|59|11|09|E|display=inline}}）；“姑马山”则是'''古迈莱角'''（{{lang|la|Ra’s Qumaylah / Ras Gumaila}}{{coord|21|56|54|N|59|39|09|E|display=inline}}），亦作'''艾西莱角'''（{{lang|la|Ra’s Aşīlah}}）。<ref>{{Cite journal|author=周运中|url=http://www.globalhistory.cn/ar.htm?opType=download&id=8a828088571be688015746ee76bd0001&tn=1519431100000|title=郑和下西洋阿拉伯海航线考|journal=暨南史学|year=2012|volume=7|pages=132-146|access-date=2019-01-14|archive-date=2019-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114210309/http://www.globalhistory.cn/ar.htm?opType=download&id=8a828088571be688015746ee76bd0001&tn=1519431100000|dead-url=no}}</ref>从舍杰尔角可以看见'''拜尼贾比尔山'''（{{lang|la|Jabal Banī Jābir}}），此山亦属于东哈杰尔山脉。古迈莱角西南方约8千米处有一座'''古迈莱山'''（{{lang|la|Jabal Qumaylah}}{{coord|21|56|05|N|59|34|55|E|display=inline}}）。<ref>{{Cite book | author = National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency | title = Red Sea and the Persian Gulf | edition = 11th Edition | series = Pub. 172 Sailing Directions (Enroute) | location = Annapolis, MD, USA | publisher = ProStar Publications | date = 2006 | pages = 157 | ISBN = 9781577857556 | url = https://books.google.fi/books?id=3jHUwGEbjNQC&printsec=frontcover | language = en | access-date = 2019-01-14 | archive-date = 2019-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190114210308/https://books.google.fi/books?id=3jHUwGEbjNQC&printsec=frontcover | dead-url = no }}</ref>

